09:41.960 --> 09:43.792
This is a preliminary hearing
on the case...

09:43.960 --> 09:47.715
<i>...of The People of the State of California
v. William Carlos Ramirez.</i>

09:47.880 --> 09:50.714
Case number A64-9725.

09:50.880 --> 09:52.792
Counsel will state your names.

09:52.960 --> 09:55.395
People are represented
by Michael Wesley.

09:55.880 --> 09:59.715
Roman J. Israel, Esquire,
on behalf of Mr. Ramirez.

09:59.880 --> 10:04.079
