to obey an erroneous court decision.

11:28.800 --> 11:30.359
You tell me to wait.
In my experience...

11:31.800 --> 11:33.075
Okay.

11:33.280 --> 11:34.760
Find you in contempt.

11:34.960 --> 11:37.919
Is there anything else
you'd like to add before I set fine?

11:43.040 --> 11:45.271
<i>I told you to just get continuances.</i>

11:45.440 --> 11:47.113
