it just doesn't seem possible.

16:42.480 --> 16:44.517
I'll take over. Ahem.

16:45.560 --> 16:49.952
No, you're not capable
of continuing the practice.

16:50.120 --> 16:52.760
On your contempt fine, we can argue
extreme emotional distress...

16:52.920 --> 16:54.593
- ...and hope for a reduction.
- Right.

16:54.760 --> 16:59.391
But I'll take over because in the
architecture of this firm, I am a pillar.

17:00.640 --> 17:03.360
Yes, and, Roman,
I'd hoped to reward you for that.

17:03.520 --> 17:05.193
