17:06.920 --> 17:09.719
- What does that mean?
- That means hope don't get the job done.

17:15.160 --> 17:17.038
Is it ego...

17:17.200 --> 17:19.192
...or delusion?

17:19.960 --> 17:21.872
Honestly, I...

17:22.800 --> 17:26.191
I never paid enough attention to you.

17:27.160 --> 17:31.473
This place runs more like
a charity service than a law firm.

17:31.640 --> 17:34.109
