17:37.240 --> 17:40.597
...his family, can no longer afford it.

17:40.760 --> 17:42.877
We're clearing the books.

17:43.080 --> 17:44.912
We're handing this off to George.

17:48.760 --> 17:50.991
Roman, I'm sorry.

17:53.880 --> 17:55.155
God, help me.

17:56.080 --> 17:58.117
Yeah, just tell him to wait.

18:00.400 --> 18:03.632
No, just tell him to wait.
I'll be there in 30. Less.

18:03.800 --> 18:06.793
- All right. One sec, one sec.
- So you have...?

18:06.960 --> 18:08.553
- I'll talk to him.
- Uh-huh.

18:28.320 --> 18:30.232
I'm sorry, man.

18:30.400 --> 18:32.119
I feel for you.

18:36.400 --> 18:38.756
This where the Bulldog did his work?

18:43.080 --> 18:44.799
What a mind.

18:44.960 --> 18:47.998
He was great in the seat
and great on his feet.

18:49.520 --> 18:52.080
Jesus, didn't he ever
throw anything away?

18:52.880 --> 18:56.430
My secretary's gonna call.
She'll be point on this.

18:57.040 --> 18:58.315
What do you use?

18:58.480 --> 19:00.915
LegalPRO? Quicken?

19:02.680 --> 19:03.716
