19:03.880 --> 19:07.271
Status on every case,
depositions, investigations...

19:07.720 --> 19:09.791
- ...conferences.
- What, on cards?

19:10.000 --> 19:11.150
You're kidding.

19:11.320 --> 19:14.154
I'm not helping you fast-plead
just so you can get a fee.

19:14.320 --> 19:17.518
Well, I'm in court every day.
I fight hard for my clients.

19:18.000 --> 19:19.320
You're a low-flying bee.

19:20.320 --> 19:23.757
- Is that what William said about me?
- William never mentioned you.

19:23.920 --> 19:26.116
- What's that about, then?
- Fact.

19:26.280 --> 19:28.715
Recorded fact, every case.

19:28.880 --> 19:30.758
Organized and available.

19:30.920 --> 19:34.630
And you can fact-check that
if you'd like on your legal Quicken.

19:34.800 --> 19:36.393
I don't have time for this.

19:36.560 --> 19:38.950
My office will call
to coordinate going forward.

19:39.120 --> 19:40.793
Let's watch him now.

19:40.960 --> 19:42.553
Young George.

