I'm quite confident of my recollections.

20:19.040 --> 20:21.555
Well, my win-loss record is
above 90 percent.

20:21.720 --> 20:23.632
That's false and misleading.
That's only if you count...

20:23.800 --> 20:25.792
...your three years as a prosecutor.

20:26.760 --> 20:29.195
Well, William thought highly enough
to bring me in.

20:29.360 --> 20:31.192
Believe me, I'm going to find out why.

20:46.560 --> 20:47.960
Roman. Hey, Roman.

20:50.400 --> 20:51.959
Where you going?

20:52.760 --> 20:55.355
- Where you going?
- MLK.

20:56.000 --> 20:57.673
Come on, I'll give you a ride.

20:58.760 --> 21:00.160
