21:01.480 --> 21:02.960
Come on, Roman.

21:05.240 --> 21:07.038
I just want to talk.

21:13.360 --> 21:16.114
William taught a term at Loyola.
That's where we met.

21:16.280 --> 21:17.794
I was, uh, top of my class.

21:18.720 --> 21:20.791
Potential's a bitch.

21:21.480 --> 21:25.474
Well, I'll tell you what's not, is having
four offices and 60 people working for you.

21:25.680 --> 21:27.478
He picked me
because I tossed him work.

21:27.680 --> 21:30.991
You know, loser cases I didn't want,
or I was too busy to handle.

21:31.160 --> 21:34.756
