for every single case I gave him.

21:59.880 --> 22:00.916
Bullshit.

22:01.080 --> 22:03.037
I have the records.

22:03.200 --> 22:05.715
You've been untouched
by the messy business...

22:05.880 --> 22:07.792
...of running
a small criminal-defense firm.

