26:50.360 --> 26:51.794
Uh...

26:52.840 --> 26:55.833
I chose cause over ambition.

26:56.000 --> 26:59.994
I could've joined one of the big firms
like the rest of them and been seduced.

27:00.160 --> 27:04.120
But I was inspired by Mr. Jackson.
I went to work for him. You can...

27:04.720 --> 27:07.554
There's a detailed, uh, record
of all of our victories.

27:07.720 --> 27:09.518
Civil-rights victories on there.

27:09.680 --> 27:11.751
As for my personal life,
at a certain point...

27:11.920 --> 27:14.310
...I had to decide whether to have
a family or career. I couldn't do both.

27:14.480 --> 27:17.518
So I stayed on the front lines.
Now, I'm offering...

27:19.880 --> 27:22.031
...at this time...

27:23.160 --> 27:25.072
...to work...

27:25.600 --> 27:27.557
...exclusively...

27:28.000 --> 27:30.037
...as your, um...

27:30.800 --> 27:32.996
...long-haul, three-dimensional...

27:33.160 --> 27:34.833
...revolutionary...

27:35.000 --> 27:36.832
...in-house, uh...

27:38.040 --> 27:40.396
...full-time, paid advocate.

27:47.760 --> 27:49.956
Mr. Israel, we're all volunteers here.

27:50.520 --> 27:55.549
Our few salaried staff work out of D. C.

27:56.200 --> 28:00.433
I'd go to interview,
but I'm precluded for pecuniary reasons.

28:00.600 --> 28:04.389
Money of late's been
a motivating factor in my life.

28:04.560 --> 28:06.119
Well...

28:06.440 --> 28:08.272
...be that as it may...

28:08.440 --> 28:10.557
...positions are filled.

28:13.080 --> 28:15.117
Look, I'm well worth having in this thing.

28:15.280 --> 28:17.351
I have no doubt of that.

28:17.520 --> 28:19.591
Because there's something
to be fired up about.

28:19.800 --> 28:22.759
We are, believe me.

28:24.080 --> 28:26.800
Ah. Well, I'll, um...

28:29.080 --> 28:31.754
...go through William's Rolodex.
Thank you, uh...

28:33.280 --> 28:34.600
...for your time.

28:38.040 --> 28:41.078
You know, if you're interested
in volunteering...

28:41.280 --> 28:43.237
...we're having a meeting next week.

28:43.400 --> 28:45.710
Uh, we could use someone
with your legal expertise.

28:45.880 --> 28:49.874
- Perhaps you could give a talk.
- I'd like that. Here's my card.

28:51.080 --> 28:53.993
I crossed out the office address.

28:54.160 --> 28:58.518
