28:58.680 --> 29:00.034
I'll probably just text you.

29:00.200 --> 29:02.669
I can do that, I think.

29:03.080 --> 29:05.151
- Thank you.
- Yeah. Thank you.

29:05.320 --> 29:06.674
Right on.

29:13.040 --> 29:15.032
What a freak.

29:15.200 --> 29:17.840
You stand on his shoulders.

29:27.640 --> 29:32.476
<i>Good afternoon. Yeah,
my name is Roman J. Israel, Esquire.</i>

29:32.640 --> 29:34.632
<i>Yeah, Israel. Yes.</i>

29:34.800 --> 29:37.110
<i>Yes, like the... Like...
