29:37.280 --> 29:41.160
I'm an attorney, civil-rights attorney.
I was inquiring about a possible job...

29:41.320 --> 29:42.674
Uh, yes, ma'am.

29:42.880 --> 29:44.633
Right, if I... If...

29:44.840 --> 29:47.071
<i>Right, if I had a job,
I wouldn't be calling you.</i>

29:47.240 --> 29:49.391
<i>That's why I'm calling.
I don't have... Hello?</i>

29:49.600 --> 29:53.594
<i>- -C-K-S-O-N. And I'd like to speak to
