29:53.760 --> 29:55.080
<i>Yeah, I'll reach out again.</i>

29:55.240 --> 29:57.800
<i>In case any jobs come up,
I'd appreciate a call back.</i>

29:57.960 --> 30:00.714
<i>Yeah, good morning.
My name is Roman J. Israel, Esquire.</i>

30:00.880 --> 30:02.075
<i>I can send you my résumé.</i>

30:02.240 --> 30:04.960
<i>I was with William Henry Jackson.
