30:55.760 --> 30:58.036
Derrell didn't know
that he was going to do that.

30:58.200 --> 30:59.919
Of course. We completely understand.

31:00.080 --> 31:01.878
Derrell was not the shooter.

31:02.040 --> 31:05.670
It's our job to prove how uncomplicit
he was in the actual murder.

31:05.880 --> 31:08.952
The way this will work is
Roman's gonna be the point person.

31:09.120 --> 31:11.999
And you were very, very wise
to retain private counsel.

31:12.160 --> 31:14.834
I'm not gonna lie to you,
Derrell's got a mountain to climb.

31:15.000 --> 31:16.798
It's imperative he receives
the best defense.

31:17.320 --> 31:19.357
I can promise you
that's what he'll get here.

31:22.040 --> 31:24.635
- I had to mortgage my house.
- Oh, I'm sorry.

31:24.800 --> 31:27.190
- I don't like lawyers.
- Ha. Me either.

31:27.400 --> 31:28.720
I understand.

31:28.880 --> 31:31.270
If I don't get answers to my questions...

31:31.440 --> 31:33.033
...if I don't see results...

31:33.240 --> 31:35.914
...if I see padded shit popping up
in my bill...

31:36.120 --> 31:38.271
...I will fire your ass.

31:38.840 --> 31:40.672
I'm putting up my house.

31:40.840 --> 31:42.638
I understand.

31:44.840 --> 31:46.957
You always dress like that?

31:47.160 --> 31:49.117
Uh, well, uh...

31:49.840 --> 31:53.072
...in lieu of wardrobe, I have a reputation
as a dedicated advocate.

31:53.240 --> 31:55.232
Let me give you my card.
If there's any questions...

31:55.400 --> 31:57.232
...concerns,
anything you want to talk about...

31:57.400 --> 31:59.995
...free of charge, I'm here.
I'm available for you.

32:00.160 --> 32:01.594
It's not the crossed-out number.

32:01.760 --> 32:04.400
It's the number
above the crossed-out number.

32:04.560 --> 32:06.756
- What's "Esquire" mean?
- Uh...

32:06.920 --> 32:09.310
It's a designation, uh...

32:09.480 --> 32:10.709
...in the legal arena.

32:10.880 --> 32:12.792
It's like...

32:12.960 --> 32:14.394
...a title of dignity.

32:14.560 --> 32:17.792
Slightly above "gentleman,"
below "knight."

32:23.760 --> 32:24.796
Yes.

32:27.320 --> 32:28.640
Come in.

32:29.080 --> 32:32.152
Roman, I'd like you to meet James Lee.
Jim, this is Roman Israel.

32:32.320 --> 32:34.437
- He'll be working closely with me on this.
- Hi.

32:34.640 --> 32:35.710
Please sit down, Roman.

32:36.640 --> 32:39.109
Roman's a terrific attorney.
We're lucky to have him.

32:39.560 --> 32:42.758
Jim's wife Mari was cited last night
for felony DUI hit and run...

32:42.920 --> 32:45.435
...with added charges
for reckless driving and injury.

32:45.600 --> 32:48.559
The way this will work is
Roman's gonna be the point person.

32:48.720 --> 32:50.757
You were very wise
to retain private counsel.

32:50.920 --> 32:54.311
Mari's... She's gonna need,
and deserves, the best defense possible.

32:54.480 --> 32:56.870
We're gonna make sure
she gets exactly that.

33:08.000 --> 33:09.957
From George.

