You work here?

34:25.920 --> 34:27.797
Yes, sir, I do.

34:28.639 --> 34:30.154
Jessie Salinas.

34:30.320 --> 34:32.437
Supervising attorney.

34:32.920 --> 34:35.480
Roman J. Israel. I'm the new guy.

34:36.280 --> 34:39.000
