34:43.280 --> 34:44.918
You're tourists.

34:51.400 --> 34:53.835
I'll see you around, Israel.

35:02.240 --> 35:04.835
Roman.

35:07.480 --> 35:08.596
Jesus.

35:09.240 --> 35:11.311
