37:40.920 --> 37:43.879
You stick to clients,
you stick to memoranda only. That's it.

37:44.040 --> 37:45.599
Nothing else, under no conditions.

37:46.200 --> 37:49.318
Now, you have
any more pressing opinions...

37:49.840 --> 37:51.399
...you share them with me.

37:54.560 --> 37:56.791
Don't come in tomorrow without a suit.

38:05.800 --> 38:07.200
Okay.

