38:43.160 --> 38:44.913
All right. From now on...

38:45.080 --> 38:47.879
...everything we discuss
will be confidential.

38:48.600 --> 38:50.034
I gotta be careful.

38:50.480 --> 38:53.439
- Is somebody threatening you?
