38:53.920 --> 38:56.355
Okay? I just went in.

38:56.560 --> 38:58.631
I didn't know what he was gonna do.

38:58.800 --> 39:02.510
- You gave a statement to the police.
- Yeah, I asked for a lawyer.

39:02.680 --> 39:04.512
And before that...

39:04.680 --> 39:08.117
...after they read you your rights,
you continued to talk to the detective.

39:08.600 --> 39:10.080
They said you said...

39:10.520 --> 39:12.477
...that you saw Carter Johnson
with a gun.

39:13.160 --> 39:15.038
I didn't know he was gonna use it.

39:15.200 --> 39:17.476
Knowing he had a gun
when you entered the store...

39:17.640 --> 39:19.597
...that's aiding and abetting.

39:19.760 --> 39:21.513
Criteria for first-degree murder.

39:21.680 --> 39:25.674
CJ. CJ shot the clerk.

39:27.160 --> 39:28.276
All right? I saw it.

39:29.080 --> 39:32.073
