39:35.040 --> 39:39.398
Now, we can talk to the DA.
See what they'll offer for your testimony.

39:40.880 --> 39:42.519
Probation.

39:43.800 --> 39:45.792
Best you can hope for is a...

39:45.960 --> 39:49.032
...possible reduction
to second-degree murder.

39:53.280 --> 39:55.158
Right over here.

39:55.320 --> 39:58.199
Have a seat if you're so scared, man.

39:59.560 --> 40:01.756
Look, I know where CJ's holed up.

